install/.title: 安装
install/.body:
Install
npm install zx-ui -S

Quick Start
import Vue from 'vue'
import Zxui from 'zx-ui'
import 'zx-ui/lib/zxhuan.css' 
Vue.use(Zxui)

Look at Examples
git clone https://gitee.com/zxhuan/vue-zx-ui.git
cd vue-zx-ui
npm install
npm run start
